{"tid":854277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強開電梯門害岳父摔死遭疑謀殺 女婿淚：忘記爸爸了","createTime":"2018-10-09T08:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T10:56:03.000Z","uid":179810,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f0abcd3fd6fff79968f2dec74c2e0fad98659b66","tid":854277,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZGQtBOw2PS0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZGQtBOw2PS0&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=274423a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZGQtBOw2PS0</a><br />\n電梯若故障了，絕對不要擅自開啟。大陸日前曝光一段影片，只見一名女婿擅自打開電梯門，導致後方的岳父未注意，從8公尺高處墜落至電梯井死亡，而許多網友看過影片後，紛紛質疑女婿疑似是故意的，但該名女婿跳出來表示，當天是為了確認電梯是否故障，卻忘了爸爸就在身後。<br />\n<br />\n根據《澎湃新聞》報導，事發於黔東南州岑鞏縣一處社區，當時女婿先是用鑰匙，自行轉開電梯門，豈料後方的岳父不清楚狀況，一腳踩進去後墜落身亡，影片在網路上流傳，引發網友熱烈討論，有人懷疑女婿為何會有電梯鑰匙，懷疑岳父死因不單純。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-10-09/450/20181009002264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-10-09%2F450%2F20181009002264.jpg&h=b085fc41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-10-09/450/20181009002266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-10-09%2F450%2F20181009002266.jpg&h=f2a0fb3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-10-09/450/20181009002267.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-10-09%2F450%2F20181009002267.jpg&h=3e0afba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而該名周姓女婿受訪時表示，9月24日當天中午，他將岳父接回家中過中秋，隨後岳父因表示，想去附近探訪親戚，恰好對方的家正是他上班地點，他在業務公司擔任水電工，平時對電梯進行檢查與維修，因此就陪同岳父一起前往。<br />\n<br />\n但在等電梯時，周姓女婿發現右邊的電梯面板，疑似出現了狀況，電梯箭頭不停地閃，「然後我就掏鑰匙把門打開檢查，一打開我就看前面去了，就把爸爸（岳父）忘記了，我沒想到後面有人，是我爸爸（岳父）」，而他當時也反應不及，想要去拉人時，人卻已掉下去了，對此也感到非常難過。<br />\n<br />\n但許多網友仍抱持懷疑，表示「反正我個人認為是間接的謀殺」、「才幾秒鐘就能把岳父忘記，是看到電梯就想修嗎？有這麼敬業？」、「電梯鑰匙，是專業人員才有的。不知道擰開電梯者，從哪來弄的電梯鑰匙？如果有人想要謀害人，使用這種方式，將會十分隱蔽」。"},{"pid":"1cb76effcbf5f79c7cb05703352e5352071a98c2","tid":854277,"uid":81113,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:13:45.000Z","msg":"身為電梯維修員<br />\n<br />\n有鎖鑰響身上，係好合理既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fb5135c447bdec34e154b65b67c976b8f0e370","tid":854277,"uid":987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"又唔識整，打開黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec2d5147604763784433fd275c4880e8e464fe8","tid":854277,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:19:23.000Z","msg":"合法殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc9c84f00768f753fc62d2f06a097d2586b64fa","tid":854277,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:28:28.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁撚on9"},{"pid":"2abf160dbaafaa3a30d1eb13a8839e77ba525494","tid":854277,"uid":6959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c3062d59787bf402699e2262766e6b610a7423e","tid":854277,"uid":34189,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"06fb5135c447bdec34e154b65b67c976b8f0e370","tid":854277,"uid":987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"又唔識整，打開黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:32:22.000Z","msg":"行規嚟,就好似架車打柴都一定要開車頭蓋望吓"},{"pid":"5f08cd50eddbe70f07cd74451903d287eb63aced","tid":854277,"uid":129622,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8c3062d59787bf402699e2262766e6b610a7423e","tid":854277,"uid":34189,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"06fb5135c447bdec34e154b65b67c976b8f0e370","tid":854277,"uid":987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"又唔識整，打開黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"